      • onRightClick

        public CustomItem.Result onRightClick(org.bukkit.entity.Player player)
        Code functionality for custom items for when the player right clicks.
        Parameters:
        player - Player who clicked
        Returns:
        Returns whether to continue with intended behavior of the item. Returning false will continue the item's normal behavior. Returning true will override it.

      • onLeftClick

        public CustomItem.Result onLeftClick(org.bukkit.entity.Player player)
        Code functionality for custom items for when the player left clicks. Intended for use in customizing that item. For example, left click and it brings up a menu for the item.
        Parameters:
        player - Player who clicked
        Returns:
        Returns whether to continue with intended behavior of the item. Returning false will continue the item's normal behavior. Returning true will override it. In most cases this just prevents breaking blocks (When returned as true)
